Osɔfo '''Francis Amenu''' enye Mɔɖeretɔ na  [[Presbyteria Nyanyui Hame le Ghana]] la ƒe General Assembly.

==Sukudede==
Osɔfo Amenu de Osɔfo suku le [[:en:Trinity Theological Seminary|Trinity College]] le [[Legon]] le [[Ghana]].<ref>[http://ttsem.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=category&sectionid=4&id=16&Itemid=44 Trinity Theological Seminary]</ref> Emegbe la, evayi de  [[:en:Christian Theological Seminary|Christian Theological Seminary]], si le [[Indianapolis]] le  [[United States]].<ref>[http://db.ghanaian-chronicle.com/thestory.asp?id=8112&title=EP%20Church%20ends%2067th%20Synod EP Church ends 67th Synod …with election of new Moderator and Clerk of General Assembly]</ref>

==Mawunya dɔwɔwɔ==
Le Osɔfo Amenu ƒe ɖoɖo megbe la, ewɔ dɔ le nutome vovovowo. Enye osɔfo na Accra New Town hamea eye enɔ [[Ho]] hã. Hamea ɖoe ɖe ablotsi eye wò vayi nɔ [[London]] le [[United Kingdom]] alo Iŋglisiawo de abe Ghanatɔwo ƒe osɔfo ene.<ref>[http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/artikel.php?ID=38441 Ghana Home Page]</ref><ref>[http://www.bmcdirectory.org/agency_detail.php?uid=98 Black Majority Churches UK]</ref> Ewɔ dɔ kple [[United Reformed Church]] le afima<ref>[http://www.geocities.com/ccom_africa_forum/doc_files/030427Africa_Forum_Hamburg_FrancisAmenuDevotion.htm Churches Commission on Mission]</ref> tso ƒe 1999 me vaseɖe ƒe 2003 me. Egbɔ va Ghana le 2003 me eye wovayi ɖu osɔfo na Madina hamea.<ref>[http://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/religion/artikel.php?ID=149050 Highest E.P Church decision-making body now General Assembly]</ref>
Osɔfo Amenu nɔ nufiam le Trinity Theological Seminary le Legon<ref>[http://ttsem.net/index.php?option=com_content&task=category&sectionid=4&id=16&Itemid=44 Adjunct Lecturers, Trinity Theological Seminary]</ref> kpakple [[EP University]] yeyea si le [[Ho, Ghana|Ho]].<ref>[http://db.ghanaian-chronicle.com/thestory.asp?id=8112&title=EP%20Church%20ends%2067th%20Synod EP Church ends 67th Synod …with election of new Moderator and Clerk of General Assembly]</ref>

Woɖo Osɔfo Amenu Mɔɖeretɔ le hamea ƒe synod 67lia le Ho le Dasiamime le ƒe 2008 me.<ref>[http://news.myjoyonline.com/news/200808/19799.asp My Joy Online]</ref>

